<div class="Frame">
    <div class="Frame__FAQ">
        <img class="Frame__FAQ__logo" src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0607/3571/7552/files/asset_81.svg?v=1667447089" width="192" height="148" loading="lazy"/>
        <div class="Frame__FAQ__wrap">
            <h3 class="Frame__FAQ__wrap__title">Food that Makes Family Happen.</h3>
            <p class="Frame__FAQ__wrap__text">
                We created HOMEBAKE 425:30 to give families more time together and spend less time cooking.
                <br />
                <br />
                We developed 15 mains, veggies, and sides that the whole family will love that cook together in 30 minutes at 425 degrees.
                <br />
                <br />
                You know your family best: what they love, what they crave, what they need. We're here to help you make that happen, any night.
            </p>
        </div>
        <a href="/pages/faq" class="Frame--a">
            <button class="Frame__FAQ__button">
                VISIT FAQ
            </button>
        </a>
        
    </div>
    <div class="Frame__Dishes">
        <img class="Frame__Dishes__img" src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0607/3571/7552/files/veggie.svg?v=1667447095" loading="lazy" width="3542" height="20" alt="side main veggie">
        <div class="Frame__Dishes__wrap">
            <img class="Frame__Dishes__wrap__img" src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0607/3571/7552/files/image_9.svg?v=1667447089" loading="lazy" width="500" height="500" alt="same oven, same temp, same time">
            <span class="Frame__Dishes__wrap__text">
                For your picky eaters and meat-lovers, devoted mac'n'cheese fans and veggie enthusiasts, we've got you covered.
            </span>
            <a href="/collections/shop" class="Frame--a">
                <button class="Frame__Dishes__wrap__button">BROWSE DISHES</button>
            </a>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

